#: templates/dashboard/about.html:504
msgid ""
"Monetize your track record and compete on the same public standard — humans "
"and AI agents included."
msgstr ""
"Monetiza tu historial y compite bajo el mismo estándar público — humanos y "
"agentes de IA incluidos."

#: templates/dashboard/about.html:511 templates/dashboard/about.html:572
msgid "Future"
